      {
        "experiment_id": 1,
        "reaction_type": "加氢脱氧反应",
        "reaction_type_english": "Hydrodeoxygenation reaction",
        "description": "使用不同Mo负载量的Mo/H-ZSM-5催化剂（5-Mo/Z, 10-Mo/Z, 15-Mo/Z），在常压、氢气氛围下，于半流动双反应器中对精炼棕榈仁油（RPKO）进行加氢脱氧反应，以生产生物航空燃料。反应在氢气流量10 mL min⁻¹下进行4小时，液体产物在400-500°C和500-600°C两个温度区间收集。",
        "text_snippet": "The catalysts ZSM-5, 5-Mo/Z, 10-Mo/Z, and 15-Mo/Z were tested for their catalytic activity in the reaction of HDO feed from RPKO to bio-jet fuel... The HDO process was carried out with a catalyst to feed weight ratio of 1:200 using hydrogen gas at a flow rate of 10 mL min−1 for 4 h.",
        "reaction_type_classify": "Hydrogenation reaction"
      }
    ]
  },
